; GPGL Command File
; Description: Position test - draws 3 cross marks
; Tool: Pen (Tool 2)
;
; Marks at:
;   Cross 1: (10mm, 10mm) from origin
;   Cross 2: (100mm, 10mm)
;   Cross 3: (10mm, 100mm)
;
; Note: 1 SU = 0.05mm, so 10mm = 200 SU
;

; Setup
FN0
SO0
J2
!10,2
FX5,2

; Cross 1 at (10mm, 10mm)
M200,150
D200,250
M150,200
D250,200

; Cross 2 at (100mm, 10mm)
M200,1950
D200,2050
M150,2000
D250,2000

; Cross 3 at (10mm, 100mm)
M2000,150
D2000,250
M1950,200
D2050,200

; Return home
H
